
 INSTALLATION ON THE UNIX PLATFORM
 ---------------------------------

 To install KTS, you will need:

  * make
  * an ANSI C compiler
  * a development environment in form of development libraries and C
    header files
  * a supported Unix operating system
  * automake, autoconf etc. for svn user

 Quick Start
 -----------

 If you want to just get on with it, do:

  $ ./configure
  $ make

 If you want to rebuild it with the svn version, do:

  $ automake
  $ autoconf
  $ ./configure
  $ make

 Please see detail instructions at http://wiki.kldp.org/wiki.php/KTS
